	  #87217, that fixes #433332 entitled 
	  "witch mouse pointer to 'busy' cursor when gdb is running"
	  The patch was made by Jonathon Jongsma <jjongsma@gnome.org>.

2007-05-19 Dodji Seketeli <dodji@gnome.org>

